data.description: This exceptional estate is nestled on a private, 2.35-acre wooded lot, in the highly sought-after South River Colony featuring a private golf course, community restaurant, gym, swimming pool, and tennis club all within minutes of downtown Annapolis. Showcasing meticulous updates and stylish design, this home invites comfort and sophistication. With 6 bedrooms(5 en suite), a true gourmet kitchen, and a basement with a wet bar, gym with sauna, and sprawling entertainment room and office, every aspect of premium living is fulfilled. Step outside to discover the remarkable screened porch that gracefully overlooks the patio, basketball/pickleball court, and a built-in gas fire pit. Purchase with peace of mind knowing the entire 30 year shingled roof, gutter system, 3-zone HVAC, water treatment system, two water heaters, washer/dryer and laundry room built-ins are all newly installed. The enchanting primary bathroom was also newly remodeled with all new vanity, tub, shower and heated tile flooring.  An oversized three-car garage, equipped with epoxy floors and an electric car charger is room and then some for your vehicles, mowers, and tools. This home has been lovingly cared for.  Every detail has been carefully designed to invite, relax, and welcome.  Please schedule a visit and experience the perfect blend of luxury and leisure -possible assumable mortgage for VA-eligible buyers.
